ğŸ“Œ Project Overview

The Face Recognition Tool is a Python-based computer vision application that automatically detects and recognizes human faces using a webcam.
It compares live video frames with pre-stored known faces and identifies the person in real time.

ğŸ¯ Objectives

Detect human faces from live camera feed

Recognize known individuals accurately

Display name on detected face

(Optional) Mark attendance with date & time

